Package edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.model.rdf.vocabulary

Contains different vocabulary

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnoVocab
    This class provides the vocabulary for annotations of the W3C (from http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#).
    AsVocab
    This class provides the vocabulary ActivityStreams (from http://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#).
    DcTermsVocab
    This class provides the vocabulary for dc-terms (http://dublincore.org/documents/dcmi-terms/).
    LdpVocab
    This class provides the vocabulary for annotations of the W3C (from http://www.w3.org/ns/ldp#).
    RdfSchemaVocab
    This class provides the vocabulary for RDF schema (https://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#) this class currently only implements the needed "label"
    RdfVocab
    This class provides the vocabulary for RDF syntax (http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#).
    WapVocab
    This class provides the vocabulary for this Project (from http://dem.scc.kit.edu/wapserv/ns#).
